==English==
[[Image:Aronia prunifolia0.jpg|thumb|right|200px|The purple '''chokeberry''' is a hybrid of the red and black '''chokeberries'''.]]

===Etymology===
{{compound|choke|berry}}, describing the [[astringency]] of the fruits, which are [[inedible]] when [[raw]].

===Noun===
{{en-noun|chokeberries}}
# Either of two species in ''[[Aronia]]'', formerly and sometimes in ''[[Photinia]]'', [[deciduous]] [[shrub]]s, native to Russia and eastern [[North America]] and most commonly found in wet woods and swamps. 
# The [[fruit]] of such a shrub.

